originalText.text: Just wanted to give Eddie with OBM NY a 5 star review for the video he produced for my father's limo business. OBM NY emailed us a couple of times about producing a review video and covering the production costs. Since video is quite expensive we thought it was "too good to be true". We ignored him a couple of times, but finally on his fourth email we decided to give him a chance. He did a great job producing the video for our business Krystal Night Limos. He did pay for production and our only investment was a small fee to rank on google and broadcast it on social media. Thanks Eddie for not giving up on us and sorry for give you such a hard time.  We look forward to future services and will highly recommend your company.
